==Azerbaijani==
{{az-variant|c=јатмаг|r=yatmaq|a=یاتماق}}
===Etymology===
From {{inh|az|trk-pro|*yạt-}}. Cognate with {{cog|tr|yatmak}}, {{cog|kk|жату|t=to lie}}, {{cog|uz|yotmoq|t=to lie}}.
===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|az|[jɑtˈmɑχ]}}
* {{hyphenation|az|jat|maq}}
